<li id="cite_note-Beit-Hallahmi-21"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Beit-Hallahmi_21-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Beit-Hallahmi_21-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Beit-Hallahmi_21-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Beit-Hallahmi_21-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Beit-Hallahmi_21-4"><sup><i><b>e</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFBeit-Hallahmi2014" class="citation book cs1">Beit-Hallahmi, Benjamin (2014). <i>Psychological Perspectives on Religion and Religiosity</i>. Routledge. pp.&#160;215–220. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9781317610366" title="Special:BookSources/9781317610366"><bdi>9781317610366</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Psychological+Perspectives+on+Religion+and+Religiosity&amp;rft.pages=215-220&amp;rft.pub=Routledge&amp;rft.date=2014&amp;rft.isbn=9781317610366&amp;rft.aulast=Beit-Hallahmi&amp;rft.aufirst=Benjamin&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AChristianity+and+science" class="Z3988"></span></span>
