<li id="cite_note-238"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-238">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Aechtner, Thomas."Galileo Still Goes to Jail: Conflict Model Persistence within Introductory Anthropology Materials"; and Garrett Kenney,"Why Religion Matters and the Purposes of Higher Education: A Dialogue with Huston Smith."." Zygon® 50.1 (2015): 209–226. loc=Abstract</span>
