<li id="cite_note-239"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-239">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Daub, Edward E. "Demythologizing White's Warfare of Science with Theology." American Biology Teacher 40.9 (1978): 553–56.</span>
</li>
</ol></div></div>
